<messaging:emailTemplate subject="G&H Receive Request for {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Applicant__r.Name} is pending for your approval (#{!RelatedTo.Name})" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_GnH_Request__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>        <p>Please note the following G&amp;H Receive Request is waiting for your approval/action.<br/>           다음과 같이, 외부인들로부터 제공받는 G&amp;H에 대한 요청이 귀하의 승인을 기다리고 있습니다.</p>        <table>            <tr>                <td>G&amp;H Request No (요청 번호)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Applicant Name (신청자 성명)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Applicant__r.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Department (부서)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Department__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>G&amp;H Type (G&amp;H 유형)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Type__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Receiving Date (수령 날짜)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy'-'MMM'-'d}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Benefit_Date__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Name of Donor (제공한 사람의 이름)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Offeror__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Organization of Donor (제공한 사람의 회사/조직)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Offeror_Organization__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Estimated Amount per Recipient (수령인 당 추정 금액)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###.##}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Amount_per_Recipient__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>PAX (총 인원)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_PAX__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Purpose (목적)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Purpose__c}</td>            </tr>        </table>        <p>To approve the G&amp;H Request, click this&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink> or by reply this email with keywords - APPROVE, YES, REJECT, NO<br/>           본 G&amp;H 요청을 승인하려면, 이 링크를 클릭하거나, 이메일에 APPROVE, YES, REJECT, NO 등의 키워드를 사용하여 답장하세요.</p>    </body></html></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>